source:
TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
The waiting pixie is sick and tired of waiting.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête
Cette Pixie attend depuis si longtemps que sa colère est prête à exploser.
TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_TODO_00<tab>Parler à la Pixie meneuse de jeu, à la bergerie d'Anden

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_TODO_01<tab>With the chat mode in <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Say<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, enter “Beaver” to let the hiding pixie know that the game is up.
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_TODO_01<tab>Trouver la Pixie cachée et en mode de discussion <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Dire<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, saisir “Castor<var 1D /var>!”
TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_TODO_02<tab>Retourner voir la Pixie meneuse de jeu, à la bergerie d'Anden
TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_TODO_03<tab>Retrouver la Pixie qui attend, à Lydha Lran

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_001<tab>Grrr, I am so angry right now! My friends promised that we'd play together here, but not one of them have come!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_001<tab>J'hallucine<var 1D /var>!!! Tout le monde est parti jouer à cache-cache sans moi<var 1D /var>! On avait promis d'y aller ensemble pourtant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_002<tab>Instead they're over in Anden's Airs, playing hide-and-seek! That's the only game they ever play, hmph!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_002<tab>La partie va se finir sans moi, si ça continue<var 1D /var>! Mais je peux rien y faire... Hé, mais si<var 1D /var>! T'es leur coqueluche depuis que t'es arrivé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> ici. Si tu les grondes, on m'oubliera pas pour la prochaine partie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_003<tab>I want you to march over there and give them a good scolding for me! You're respected in our village, so they'll take your words to heart!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_003<tab>Va à la bergerie d'Anden, dis-leur que tu viens de ma part et que ça se fait pas, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_004<tab>The others are over in Anden's Airs, playing hide-and-seek! Go over there and give them a good scolding for me!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_004<tab>Va à la bergerie d'Anden, dis-leur que tu viens de ma part et que ça se fait pas, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source:
TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_010...A promise? I don't recall a─
Ahhh! We completely forgot! Oh, we're so sorry!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_010<tab>Qui ça<var 1D /var>? Han<var 1D /var>! On a com<var 16 /var>plè<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment oublié<var 1D /var>! Je m'en veux... Qu'est-ce qu'on va faire<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_011<tab>We would go with you right now, but we're in the midst of a game of hide-and-seek. One of us is still hiding, and we can't well leave them behind. Will you help us search?
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_011<tab>On peut pas rentrer tout de suite en plus, il nous reste encore quelqu'un à trouver<var 1D /var>! Et si tu nous aidais à chercher<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_012<tab>Thank you! Now, when you find them, you must say the word “beaver.” It's the rules!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_012<tab>Super<var 1D /var>! Je t'explique les règles, enfin, la règle<var 1D /var>! Quand tu trouves quelqu'un, il suffit de dire<var 1D /var>: “Castor<var 1D /var>!” C'est simple, hein<var 1D /var>?
TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_013<tab>On a aucune idée d'où tu devrais chercher, mais sa cachette peut pas être très loin<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_014<tab>Our last hiding friend should be somewhere nearby. Remember, when you find them, you must say the word “beaver.” It's the rules!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_014<tab>On a aucune idée d'où tu devrais chercher, mais la cachette de notre camarade peut pas être très loin<var 1D /var>! Souviens-toi, tu dois lui dire “Castor<var 1D /var>!”, sinon la partie continue<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_SYSTEM_100_021<tab>With the chat mode in <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Say<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, use your keyboard or the software keyboard to enter “Beaver” to let the hiding pixie know that the game is up.
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_SYSTEM_100_021<tab>En mode de discussion <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Dire<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, utilisez le clavier ou le clavier virtuel pour signifier à la Pixie que vous l'avez trouvée en lui disant “Castor<var 1D /var>!”.

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_BIBAPIXIE03426_100_022<tab>(Shhh! Can't you see I'm trying to hide!?)
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_BIBAPIXIE03426_100_022<tab>Chuuuuut<var 1D /var>! Je joue à cache-cache<var 1D /var>! Tu vas me faire repérer<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_BIBAPIXIE03426_000_020Oh no, I am found!
...Wait, aren't you )) (( )) 02 /var>!? I didn't know you were playing too! This makes it even more fun, tee hee!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_BIBAPIXIE03426_000_020<tab>AH<var 1D /var>! Où... où ça<var 1D /var>!? Hein<var 1D /var>? Me dis pas que tu joues aussi, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var><var 1D /var>!? On te manquait, c'est ça<var 1D /var>?♪

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_BIBAPIXIE03426_100_030<tab>Tee hee, it was so fun being found by you! You must play hide-and-seek with us again!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_BIBAPIXIE03426_100_030<tab>Hé hé<var 1D /var>! J'ai perdu, mais comme c'était amusant de jouer avec toi, eh ben je m'en fiche<var 1D /var>! Tu me promets qu'on rejouera<var 1D /var>? S'il te plaît<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_030<tab>You did well to find our hiding friend! We would never have thought to look there!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_030<tab>Jamais on aurait pensé à aller fouiner par là-bas. Heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment qu'on t'avait avec nous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_031<tab>But come, it wouldn't do to keep our waiting friend waiting any longer. They aren't the most patient of pixies.
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_KAKUREPIXIE03426_000_031<tab>J'y pense, faut qu'on se dépêche de rentrer à Lydha Lran. Si on s'excuse pas, je connais quelqu'un qui voudra plus jamais jouer avec nous... Dis-lui qu'on arrive bientôt, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_040<tab>The others finally came, thanks to you! But what's this I hear about you playing hide-and-seek with them?
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_040<tab>Coucou, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var><var 1D /var>! Tu as raté quelque chose, j'ai eu droit à de plates excuses<var 1D /var>! J'aurais quand même bien aimé y être, c'était la partie du siècle, il paraît<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_041<tab>That's not fair! I want to be found by you too! Promise me you'll play with us again soon!
target: TEXT_LUCKZD019_03426_WAITINGPIXIE03426_000_041<tab>En plus, tu as participé<var 1D /var>! Faudra qu'on refasse ça, avec toi, moi, et tout Lydha Lran<var 1D /var>!
